popularityCurve.label: please join us in taking a stand against the war even if you can only stop by for a few minutes your presence helps make a difference those of us who regularly attend the vigil enjoy sharing news and community with each other and the encouraging honks and support from many drivers among other purposes this weekly vigil serves as a regular reminder to hundreds of people in our community those driving or walking by of our viewpoints issues and information something they rarely see in the media bring a sign or borrow one of our extras join us
